aximum entropy and dynamical modelling. Regularized\nlinear inversion with continuum light curve modelling provides a fast,\ncomplementary method for velocity-resolved reverberation mapping and is\nsuitable for use on large datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Feb 2015 21:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Aug 2015 14:33:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-23"}
