dex that is described in detail in paper II. Future statistical work,\nquantifying the uncertainties in this process, may improve the more heuristic\napproach used by early forecasting systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Feb 2015 22:37:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Mar 2015 18:38:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 12 Mar 2015 08:39:18 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2015 20:17:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
