lastic modulus of factors other than porosity could be\nevaluated. It was found that the heterogeneity of the pore structure has a\nsignificant influence on the elastic properties computed using mechanical\nsimulation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 7 Feb 2015 14:55:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-10"}
